{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472530/extras/wandering.gif?t=1721731619\" /><br>PILLORY is a surreal indie RPG set in a forgotten afterlife.<br>Engage in unique turn-based mood battles and meet strange creatures in the dark corners the Progenitors forgot about.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472530/extras/weirdos.gif?t=1721731619\" /><br>Throughout your adventure, encounter a mix of unusual allies and foes.<br>Some, like you, are lost. Others are indifferent to their eternal existence.<br>Some mean you great harm.<br><br>Combat revolves around party members proposing ideas each turn.<br>You may choose one, or reroll for a different idea, at the cost of mood.<br>Identifying enemies' weaknesses to one of the three damage types is crucial.<br><br>At extreme moods, you will lose control.<br>Managing your mood is essential in combat.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Explore an unique, surreal world.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Interact with eccentric NPCs.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Unique mood-based combat system that rewards balanced, foresightful play.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Every environment and character individually drawn and unique.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>&quot;Death&quot; makes you stronger.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>An absolutely <i>insufferable</i> side-kick.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Almost entirely made by a single person.</strong></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1721731619","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472530/page.bg.jpg?t=1721731619","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472530/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1721731619","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akama